 &lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;File | External Data | Pack Resources&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;Save&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ol&gt;</description> <link>https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Archived/Blender/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 12:08:39 +0800</pubDate> <source url="https://shenmian.github.io/notes/feed_rss_created.xml">Notes</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Archived/Blender/</guid> </item> <item> <title>Emoji</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Emoji&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;h2&gt;People&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;| | | ...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Archived/Emoji/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 12:08:39 +0800</pubDate> <source url="https://shenmian.github.io/notes/feed_rss_created.xml">Notes</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Archived/Emoji/</guid> </item> <item> <title>Qt</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Qt&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://download.qt.io/official_releases/online_installers/&#34;&gt;https://download.qt.io/official_releases/online_installers/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;```console&lt;/p&gt; &lt;blockquote&gt; &lt;p&gt;qt-unified-windows-x64-4.6.1-online.exe --mirror https://mirrors.aliyun.com...&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/blockquote&gt;</description> <link>https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Archived/Qt/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 12:08:39 +0800</pubDate> <source url="https://shenmian.github.io/notes/feed_rss_created.xml">Notes</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Archived/Qt/</guid> </item> <item> <title>论犯罪与刑罚</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;论犯罪与刑罚&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;h2&gt;刑罚的起源&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;blockquote&gt; &lt;p&gt;人们牺牲一部分自由是为了平安无扰地享受剩下的那份自由.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/blockquote&gt; &lt;p&gt;需要一种易感触 (可以通过感官感知到的) 的力量 (motivi sensibili) 来防止个人专横的心灵破坏法律, 这种力量就是刑罚. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;惩罚权&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;交给公共保存的最少量自由的结晶形成惩罚权. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Archived/%E8%AE%BA%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%91%E7%BD%9A/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 12:08:39 +0800</pubDate> <source url="https://shenmian.github.io/notes/feed_rss_created.xml">Notes</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Archived/%E8%AE%BA%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%91%E7%BD%9A/</guid> </item> <item> <title>Multi-class SVM</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Multi-class SVM&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;h2&gt;One vs another&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;Datasets: $C_1$, $C_2$, $C_3$ SVMs: 1. ($C_2$, $C_3$) vs $C_1$ 2. ($C_1$, $C_3$) vs $C_2$ 3. ($C_1$, $C_2$) vs $C_3$&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;共...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Archived/AI/Machine%20Learning%202024-4-16/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 12:08:39 +0800</pubDate> <source url="https://shenmian.github.io/notes/feed_rss_created.xml">Notes</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Archived/AI/Machine%20Learning%202024-4-16/</guid> </item> </channel> </rss>